 █╠┼  ║  The Madden NFL team strives every year to make what you         ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  experience on your screen as close as possible to what          ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  actually takes place on the field. That's why Madden NFL 11     ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  has taken a back-to-basics approach with the mantra "Simpler.   ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  Quicker. Deeper." An all-new GameFlow system makes play         ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  calling simpler by putting you in the helmet of an NFL          ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  quarterback, allowing you to execute and change an authentic    ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  game plan, one play at a time, based on your situation.         ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  You'll spend more time on the field and less time in the        ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  playbook with the quicker game time, reduced from 60 minutes    ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  to 30 minutes. And youll be able to go deeper with improved     ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  animations and control options, as well as enhanced online      ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  functionality and a new broadcast and audio presentation that   ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  delivers the NFL experience that NFL fans have come to          ║   ┼╣█
 █╠┼  ║  expect.                                                         ║   ┼╣█
